OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 28 JUN
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1981FThe BBC announces a major
OL,7,Fshake-up of the presentation of its TV
OL,8,Fnews programmes.
OL,9,
OL,10,FAs well as a complete overhaul of
OL,11,Fstudio sets and title sequences, Peter
OL,12,FWoon, editor, TV News, took the
OL,13,Fdecision to have more journalists
OL,14,Freading the news.
OL,15,
OL,16,FThe main presenter changes:
OL,17,
OL,18,F(a) former correspondents John Humphrys
OL,19,Fand John Simpson would present the Nine
OL,20,Fo'Clock News;
OL,21,F(b) Richard Baker to present the
OL,22,FEvening News;
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
